# Top-level META-INF/ appears when Stardog JARs are extracted at the repo root
# by mistake; it never enters the classpath and shouldn't be tracked. Only the
# leading slash form applies — src/main/resources/META-INF/ is unaffected.
/META-INF/

# Local ML-model cache (e.g. fastembed onnx blobs) fetched by tests on
# first run. Multi-hundred-megabyte binaries; never tracked.
.fastembed_cache/